DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and compare the bioavailability of fenofibric acid from 2 different dosage strengths of ABT-335.
DOC.brief_title: Comparison of Fenofibric Acid Bioavailability From ABT-335 Capsules
DOC.criteria: A condition of general good health BMI 18 to 29 Currently enrolled in another clinical study Females who are pregnant or breastfeeding
